| GET    | `/product`     | Get all products   | âŒ No |
| GET    | `/product/:id` | Get product by ID  | âŒ No |
| PUT    | `/product/:id` | Update product     | âœ… Admin |
| DELETE | `/product/:id` | Delete product     | âœ… Admin |

